title: Fizarolli is an Imp and the 9 Circles of Hell Explained! Helluva Boss Episode 7 Breakdown & Analysis
author: Cartoon Universe
description:
Episode 7 of Helluva Boss gave us so much new lore! We saw the prince of Lust, Asmoedeous, also known as ozzie, we got to see Verosika return, and who knows what these 9 circles of hell may lead to!
